controls.name: INSTRUCTIONS
controls.text:
- Choose a Url.  Click Go, browser shows results
- To toggle OLE events Click Start OLE Log.
- To toggle WinMsgs, click  Start WinMsg Log.
- Start OLE log, then navigate to .xls to See Error
- To Get a Property, Type in the property name, click Get.

- With OLE Log Running, click on OIWeb radio button,
use a URL of http://\oecgi.exe\trace\?test=2, click go. OI intercepts the jump, runs it without web server.
- To Set a Property,  Type in a new value, Click Set.

- To run a function,  Type name in Send Message , put params in edit table, click send

- Replace about:blank with RICHTEXT.Richtext or DHTMLEdit.Dhtmledit
